<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='201149' id='t-201149'>In fact, I've pretty much wasted most of my life</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='203969' id='t-203969'>DJing in night clubs</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='205266' id='t-205266'>and producing pop records.</span>
