<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='241573' id='t-241573'>The other good thing about watching TED Talks,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='244368' id='t-244368'>when you see a really good one,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='246255' id='t-246255'>you kind of all of a sudden wish the speaker</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='248188' id='t-248188'>was your best friend, don't you? Like, just for a day.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='251032' id='t-251032'>They seem like a nice person.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='253027' id='t-253027'>You'd take a bike ride, maybe share an ice cream.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='256009' id='t-256009'>You'd certainly learn a lot.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='258760' id='t-258760'>And every now and then they'd chide you,</span>
