<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='264879' id='t-264879'>But then they'd remember that
you're but a mere human</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='267348' id='t-267348'>of ordinary, mortal intelligence</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='268830' id='t-268830'>that didn't finish university,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='270229' id='t-270229'>and they'd kind of forgive you,</span>
