<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='277515' id='t-277515'>Man, yeah, back to the real world,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='280253' id='t-280253'>probably Sir Ken Robinson and I</span>
